name: Cherry Cordial Heart Cake - One Slice
description: @Sugartivi | Dear art collector, this is one slice of the cherry liqueur cake, which has three dark chocolate layers inside. I bake to bring a little bit of sweetness to others, amidst our hurried, varied and sometimes difficult lives. This cake has some complicated taste memories behind it. It is in memory of all those lost to hunger. And all that we hunger for.
